@startuml state_machine
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor LightCoral
  BorderColor DarkRed
  ArrowColor DarkSlateGray
  StartColor DarkGreen
  EndColor DarkRed
}
title State Machine — AttendanceRecord Lifecycle

[*] --> NotYet : work_date created\n(shift scheduled)

NotYet --> Present     : CheckIn + CheckOut\nwithin thresholds
NotYet --> Late        : CheckIn > start + late_threshold
NotYet --> Absent      : No CheckIn by 22:00\n(AutoAbsentJob)
NotYet --> Holiday     : date in holidays table
NotYet --> DayOff      : is_day_off = 1\n(shift schedule)
NotYet --> Leave       : approved leave_request\nexists for this date

Present --> EarlyLeave    : CheckOut < end - early_threshold
Late    --> LateAndEarly  : Late + CheckOut early
Present --> Present       : HR manual edit\n(is_manual_edit = 1)
Absent  --> Present       : HR manual edit\n(retroactive correction)

Leave --> [*]       : leave period ends
Holiday --> [*]     : next working day
DayOff --> [*]      : next working day
Present --> [*]     : end of work day (final)
Late --> [*]        : end of work day (final)
EarlyLeave --> [*]  : end of work day (final)
LateAndEarly --> [*]: end of work day (final)
Absent --> [*]      : record kept for reporting

note right of NotYet
  Initial state for every
  active employee on a
  working day
end note

note right of Present
  status field in
  attendance_records
  (9 possible values)
end note

note right of Absent
  Triggered by background job
  attendance.auto_absent_hour = 22
end note

@enduml
